title: My skin
body: I haven't received my skin yet for the 10th anniversary. I got both the summoner icon and Kayle but did not receive the Riot Kayle. Can some1 help me?

replies.body: If the account in question is the one you're posting from, then it looks like you already received Riot Kayle last week.  Everything looks okay here, but let me know if you can't select her!  Let me know!
The gifts are still being handed out, and the final date to receive them has been moved to the 30th, as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us).
